1. Project Title: Social Media CRUD Application

2. Introduction: This project is a social media platform utilizing CRUD methods. It aims to enhance user engagement and connectivity.

3. Objectives: Create a seamless full-stack application. Integrate frontend and backend using React and Express.

4. Project Description: The project addresses the need for efficient social interaction online. Key features include user posts, comments, and profile management.

5. Technologies and Tools:

React for the frontend
Express for the backend
MySQL with Sequelize for database management

6. Features:
User Authentication: Secure login and registration process.
CRUD Operations: Users can create, read, update, and delete posts.
Real-time Updates: Seamless UI updates without full page reloads.

7. Implementation Plan: Development follows an agile methodology with iterative testing. Potential challenges include database management and deployment issues.

8. Testing Plan: Conduct unit testing for each feature. Use manual and automated testing strategies to identify bugs.(morgan/postman)

9. Expected Outcome: A fully functional social media application with user interaction. Success is measured by user satisfaction and engagement metrics.

